---
import videoPosterImg from '@/assets/images/bf60da9a2083.jpg';
---

<section class="section section--tint s6-benefits">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="s6-benefits__heading">Why Choose ClearLift in at Menon Medispa in Millburn?</h2>

    <p class="s6-benefits__intro">
      Experience the most advanced, comfortable, and effective skin rejuvenation treatment available. Here's what sets ClearLift apart from other options.
    </p>

    <div class="s6-benefits__grid">

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">Zero Downtime Required</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">Unlike traditional lasers or chemical peels, ClearLift allows you to return to all activities immediately after treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">Completely Pain-Free</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">Experience gentle warming sensations instead of pain. No numbing cream or anesthesia needed for comfortable treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">Quick 30-Minute Sessions</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">Fit your skin transformation into your busy schedule with efficient treatments during your lunch break.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">Safe for All Skin Types</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">ClearLift works safely on all six Fitzpatrick skin types, including darker skin tones that other treatments can't address.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">FDA-Approved Technology</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">ClearLift uses clinically proven Q-switched laser technology, backed by extensive research and safety studies.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__card">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__card-heading">Long-Lasting Results</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__card-text">Results improve over time as your skin naturally produces more collagen, with effects lasting up to 2 years.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s6-benefits__bonus">

      <div class="s6-benefits__bonus-text">
        <h3 class="s6-benefits__bonus-heading">Beyond Facial Rejuvenation</h3>
        <p class="s6-benefits__bonus-body">
          ClearLift laser technology offers remarkable results for lip enhancement and rejuvenation. This gentle, non-invasive treatment stimulates collagen production in the delicate lip area, naturally improving lip definition, reducing fine lines around the mouth, and restoring a fuller, more youthful appearance.
        </p>
        <p class="s6-benefits__bonus-body">
          The precision of ClearLift allows us to treat the lip borders and surrounding area without downtime, making it an ideal solution for those seeking subtle, natural lip enhancement without fillers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="s6-benefits__bonus-media">
        <video
          class="s6-benefits__video"
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          poster={videoPosterImg.src}
          width="480"
          height="270"
        >
          <source
            src="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/2baa5c_a1e2e08938534d2a8f421b35a9a4de05/720p/mp4/file.mp4"
            type="video/mp4"
          />
          <track kind="descriptions" />
        </video>
        <img
          src={videoPosterImg.src}
          alt="ClearLift lip enhancement treatment at Menon Medispa"
          class="s6-benefits__poster"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="480"
          height="270"
        />
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s6-benefits__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s6-benefits__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .s6-benefits__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s6-benefits__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .s6-benefits__card-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s6-benefits__card-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .s6-benefits__bonus {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .s6-benefits__bonus-text {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s6-benefits__bonus-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s6-benefits__bonus-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .s6-benefits__bonus-media {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 420px;
  }

  .s6-benefits__video {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .s6-benefits__poster {
    display: none;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .s6-benefits__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s6-benefits__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .s6-benefits__bonus {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .s6-benefits__bonus-media {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .s6-benefits__video {
      display: none;
    }

    .s6-benefits__poster {
      display: block;
    }
  }
</style>
